defaultIntroductiondefault&#xa0;
defaultOver recent years, educational inequality has risen up the political agenda, leading to Teach First being named as one of the most prestigious career choices for top graduates in the UK, and a number of successful initiatives including the London challenge. 
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
defaultNot only is this manifestly unfair, they also show that young talent is being wasted on an industrial scale. However, as research suggests, the prevalence of educational inequality is particularly apparent among white working class pupils. 
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
